## 🔑 Key Rules

**16 mandatory rules:** [.sdd-core/EXECUTION/spec/CANONICAL/rules/ia-rules.md](../../.sdd-core/EXECUTION/spec/CANONICAL/rules/ia-rules.md)

**Top 5 critical:**

1. Ports Mandatory — Use interfaces, not concrete implementations
2. Thread Isolation — Check execution-state/ for conflicts
3. Tests During Implementation — TDD, never test-after
4. No Implicit State — Verify everything before acting
5. Checkpoint After Work — Document what you implemented

---

## ✅ Before Pushing PR

```
[ ] Pre-commit hooks passed (local validation)
[ ] All tests passing (100% coverage for new code)
[ ] Checkpoint updated in execution-state/
[ ] No rule violations
[ ] Ready for review
```

